From 2c9f571b03dd250da60e61e71acfa25058089fd5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ashok Kumar <ashok2.kumar@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Oct 2023 11:53:33 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 1/1] recipes-kernel: To enable GPIO and SGPIO for Power
 Control

Jamaica/Marley
 - GPIO and SGPIO for power control
 - pin ctrl changes for BIOS -SPIx1

Signed-off-by: Ashok Kumar <ashok2.kumar@amd.com>
---
 .../boot/dts/aspeed-bmc-amd-marley-i3c.dts    | 26 +++++++++++++++----
 arch/arm/boot/dts/aspeed-bmc-amd-marley.dts   | 26 +++++++++++++++----
 2 files changed, 42 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/aspeed-bmc-amd-marley-i3c.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/aspeed-bmc-amd-marley-i3c.dts
index f8a7a095c9ad..8c9b959dca72 100644
